OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPartly cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells. Cloud will thicken
OL,7,Facross parts of Devon and Cornwall
OL,8,Fthis afternoon to give a few showers.
OL,9,FVery warm in the sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud will gradually fade to
OL,12,Fgive a fine end to the day with some
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Staying dry overnight
OL,14,Fwith clear skies and light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FBlue skies at first, before a
OL,17,Flittle cloud bubbles up through the
OL,18,Fmorning. Still plenty of sunny spells
OL,19,Fand feeling very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
